{"tid":2060090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"求成人泳班介紹","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T11:12:45.000Z","uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adfedba47a5f95282f63e7eaf880148f76c9ca93","tid":2060090,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"話說我今三十零歲，最近想keep住做運動減磅，但因為太重太肥、跑步唔係太適合，所以想學游水。<br />\n<br />\n本身自己只能自由式換到兩次氣游到半個直池，到換第三次氣個人就沉。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想睇下呢度有無巴打絲打有成人泳班推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地點最好喺新界西（元朗、天水圍、荃灣就最好）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f412678cbfe814b512ea55ca68646e54a482c98f","tid":2060090,"uid":60049,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"成人泳班<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4466fea7b694f42aa10bb0b6fd248f9dd0c0a083","tid":2060090,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"需唔需要一對一私教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45feae68bba9451ba7b4776f91c5065011186669","tid":2060090,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4466fea7b694f42aa10bb0b6fd248f9dd0c0a083","tid":2060090,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite